@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  LifeLineColor #3498DB
  ParticipantBorderColor #2C3E50
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #ECF0F1
}

title Documentation Updates Pattern Analysis

participant "Documentation\nManager" as DM
participant "Repository\nAnalyzer" as RA
participant "Semantic\nAnalyzer" as SA
participant "Knowledge\nManager" as KM

activate DM
DM -> RA: Scan documentation files
activate RA

RA -> SA: Analyze content changes
activate SA
SA --> RA: Pattern detection results
deactivate SA

RA -> KM: Update knowledge base
activate KM
KM --> RA: Knowledge base updated
deactivate KM

RA --> DM: Documentation analysis complete
deactivate RA

note right of DM
  Pattern Statistics:
  - 13 Occurrences
  - Stable trend
  - Significance: 7/10
end note

DM -> DM: Update documentation\nmetadata

note over DM, KM
  Implementation Components:
  - Test scripts
  - Session logs
  - Integration files
  - Configuration files
end note

deactivate DM

@enduml